data.title: Let's Play Borderlands: Pre-Sequel - GameCrate
data.description: Discover the story behind Borderlands 2's villain, Handsome Jack, and his rise to power in this brand new game in the Borderlands Series. Taking place between the original Borderlands and Borderlands 2, the Pre-Sequel gives you a whole lot of new gameplay featuring the genre-fusion of shooter and RPG gameplay that players can't get enough of.

data.title: Let's Play Hyrule Dynasty Warriors - GameCrate
data.description: Cut down entire legions of enemies as Link, Zelda, Midna and other characters from The Legend of Zelda franchise using over-the-top powerful Dynasty Warriors-style moves.

data.title: Let's Play Sid Meier's Civilization: Beyond Earth - GameCrate
data.description: Ever wonder what you would do if you can create your own world Beyond Earth? Travel through space with Rachel and Nicks gameplay of Civilization: Beyond Earth as they colonize new planets and build a new world!

data.title: Lets Play! Destiny - GameCrate
data.description: With mankind on the brink of extinction, join Q and Rachel in this post-apocalyptic journey seven hundred years into the future saving human civilization. This is their Destiny.

data.title: Lets Play! Nosgoth - GameCrate
data.description: Nosgoth is a free-to-play, 3rd person PVP combat game from Square Enix which is currently in closed beta. Follow Rachel and Nick as they battle vampires and try not to get bitten by the creatures of the night!

data.title: Lets Play! Surgeon Simulator - GameCrate
data.description: Two men, one patient! Join Q and Steve as they play DOCTOR on Playstation 4's Surgeon Simulator.

data.title: GameCrate & NeweggTV Mario Kart 8 Tournament
data.tags: mario kart 8, gaming, gamecrate, newegg, super mario, princess peach, racing, computer, wii u, nintendo, pc, console
data.description: The Newegg TV team and GameCrate go head to head in this thrilling Mario Kart 8 tournament! Who will be the first to be eliminated and who will rise victorious? Grab your kart and your green shells and let's get started!
